data.description: Open and inviting is what you immediately notice about this home in beautiful RoseHill subdivision and will want to make it yours.  The floorplan has 4 bedrooms downstairs in a split plan with the primary being spacious with a large bathroom with tiled shower and soaking tub and a generous closet. Upstairs you'll find a bonus bedroom with its own private bathroom.  The backyard has a covered patio with a large concrete pad extension great for entertaining, grilling or just relaxing. Don't hesitate to come see this lovely home and call it yours today!
